# Clean Architecture

## Imports permitidos

| De | Pode importar |
|----|----------------|
| `domain/` | nada externo (só TS puro) |
| `application/` | `domain/` |
| `infrastructure/` | `domain/`, libs externas |

## Fluxo

`app/api/route.ts` → `application/` → `domain/` port ← `infrastructure/` adapter

## Nova feature

`domain/foo/` → `application/foo/` → `infrastructure/foo/` → `app/api/foo/`

